root: ^!I texted Jade, asking her if she wanted to meet up.

^!Jade and I have been texting at haunting hours every night. I’ve been inquiring about her Victorian interests, while relaying my Goth-adjacent interests by sending her my favorite Goth songs. I’ve been trying to seem cool on text, but I’m not quite sure it has been coming across.
^!Jade is the coolest girl I know.
^!I made my way to her Victorian mansion, my heart racing as the thought of her filled my mind.
